    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ all--laud-ed Mar--tyrs of the__ Lord,__ lo,___ the__ earth__ con--cealed___ you__ not;__ but ra-ther Heav---en__ re-ceived__ you___ and the____ gates of Par---a---dise__ wel-comed you___ and__ o--pened. And___ as__ ye__ now__ dwell___ there--in__ ye joy-ful-ly par-take____ of__ the__ Tree___ of___ Life.__ Thus,____ in-ter-cede,___ we___ pray,__ with the Mas---ter,____ e-ven Christ the Lord,__ that He__ grant___ peace and great mer---cy___ to__ our___ souls."
    }
